(1414, 'Publish', '2010-09-30 02:27:51', '2010-11-22 15:58:34', 'Mammals', 'EDGE', '87', 'Mammalia', 'Soricomorpha', 'Soricidae', 'Cryptotis nelsoni', '', 'Nelson’s Small Eared Shrew', '9.73005188', 'CR', '5.14563711', 'This tiny mammal was believed extinct after not being seen for more than a century. Two researchers actively searched for, and rediscovered the species in 2003.', 'This species is known from only one location, and there is continuing decline in the extent and quality of its habitat.', '', 'None', 'N', 'N', 'Mexico', '', ''),
